tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE AudienceEngagement (
    engagement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    engagement_date DATE,
    likes_count INT,
    comments_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE Influencers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    followers INT,
    engagement_rate DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE Audience (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    audience_name VARCHAR(50),
    age_range VARCHAR(20),
    location VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE EngagementData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    audience_id INT,
    likes INT,
    comments INT,
    shares INT
)

CREATE TABLE posts (
    post_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    post_content TEXT,
    likes_count INT,
    comments_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE comments (
    comment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    post_id INT,
    commenter_name VARCHAR(255),
    comment_text TEXT,
    comment_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE audience_demographics (
    audience_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    age_group VARCHAR(50),
    location VARCHAR(100),
    gender VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE Influencers (
  influencer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  influencer_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  followers_count INT,
  engagement_rate FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Posts (
  post_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  influencer_id UUID,
  post_content TEXT,
  post_date TIMESTAMP,
  likes_count INT,
  comments_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE Comments (
  comment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  post_id UUID,
  commenter_name TEXT,
  comment_text TEXT,
  comment_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE Likes (
  like_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  post_id UUID,
  liker_name TEXT,
  like_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE Shares (
  share_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  post_id UUID,
  sharer_name TEXT,
  share_date TIMESTAMP
)
